{"lastModified":1752233648030,"uri":"c::8345304695::vessel::b44355e0-e4b5-11ef-a039-a3899795a2b4","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLagoon 42  “Barney”, a part of our fleet since 2020, is a roomy, stable and luxurious twin-hulled sailing catamaran. She boasts plenty of room for families and friends to spread out and enjoy their stay aboard. The lines of this good-looking boat were drawn by VPLP and Patrick le Quément. The yacht incorporates all the distinctive Lagoon features: vertical windows, a single-level cockpit and saloon, integral deck hatches and an ergonomic helm station. With light, bright and airy interiors, Lagoon 42  Barney is a true example of why catamarans are so popular lately. The large main sail area, also makes it relatively fast.\n\nBarney has an on-board WI-FI, sound entertainment system and air-conditioning both in salons and all guest cabins.  In addition to Kayak and SUP, the boat also includes a 3,5 m tender with an outboard engine of 20 HP. Families will love “Barney” for its multiple living areas. Cruising under sail has its own special allure and guests can be assured of a superb charter experience. This catamaran is available both as a bareboat and crewed charter. We can’t wait to try her under sails … and you? Hurry up with your bookings and experience nothing but the best for your luxury charter!","blueprint":{"name":"BARNEY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44355e0-e4b5-11ef-a039-a3899795a2b4::assets::1fc26be0-e4ba-11ef-ac3e-ad9aa5e8a6aa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44355e0-e4b5-11ef-a039-a3899795a2b4::assets::1ffab9f0-e4ba-11ef-ac3e-ad9aa5e8a6aa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44355e0-e4b5-11ef-a039-a3899795a2b4::assets::1fe92dc0-e4ba-11ef-ac3e-ad9aa5e8a6aa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44355e0-e4b5-11ef-a039-a3899795a2b4::assets::1fd6b730-e4ba-11ef-ac3e-ad9aa5e8a6aa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b4435